      "comment": "MORAINE ARNIE (6) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at this track behind Moraine Grace (22.81) in a Grade 5. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Key chance in this line up. PAW YAZ (3) was a winner (23.54) at Horsham two back but out of the placings last time when 6th at Sale. Can do much better this time. ASTON FUMIKO (4) has a strong record here with two wins and a minor from four starts. Below best last time at Shepparton (22.96) in a Grade 5, finishing a 10 length eighth. Can hit the frame with the right run. PAW VERITY (2) cannot be underestimated.",
